1. **Facial Recognition Enhancement using CGAN (built, deployed):** Built a Conditional GAN pipeline in Python (data preprocessing, adversarial training, L2/SSIM evaluation) that converts hand-drawn eyewitness sketches into photorealistic color faces to aid suspect identification; deployed as a real-time Streamlit web app where users upload a sketch and instantly get a generated realistic face.
2. **Emotion Detection using CNN (built):** Trained a convolutional neural network in Python to classify facial expressions into distinct emotion categories from face images.
3. *GitHub Repo Assistant (LangGraph + MCP, working prototype):** Built a conversational agent using LangGraph and Gemini 2.5 Flash (via OpenRouter) that connects to GitHub's official MCP server (Dockerized) alongside a custom local MCP server; lets users perform GitHub actions (repo analysis, docs, PR/issue tasks) through natural language, with built-in confirmation prompts before executing any risky GitHub operations, and persistent chat memory via LangGraph's checkpointer.
